judecian hospital in timisoara 
daniszewski a correspondent based in warsaw poland was in the 
romanian city about 30 miles east of the yugoslav border to cover 
the revolution in romania 
the consulate said it was informed about the shooting and 
daniszewskis condition by ljuba pajic a yugoslav journalist 
working for the politika expres newspaper who was with him in the 
car 
the two were ordered stopped saturday night by a group of men in 
